= Import bitmap =
* Paste bitmap into Word (yes, Word!), then copy+paste into Altium. Note, make the bitmap as large as possible in Word to achieve maximum resolution in Altium.

= Resizing/scaling polygon pours etc. =
* make union from selected objects
* right click -> Unions -> Resize union

= Non-obvious keyboard shortcuts =
Ctrl + double click to open child sheet

= Cloning room layouts =
Design -> Rooms -> Copy Room Formats